title: Early Miami meet up on the 16th at 7pm?
body:
We down to meet up at "Swizzle rum bar & Drinkery" for those that come in early on the 16th? 

We can start meeting up around 7pm. Then, just figure it out from there depending on how many of us Gambling Apes show up. 
Maybe hit a casino after? 

Address: 1120 Collins Ave, Miami Beach, FL 33139
Website: https://www.swizzlerumbardrinkery.com
